= treemap_player

Treemap UI music player.

== Requirements

* Windows
* iTunes
* Ruby-Processing http://github.com/jashkenas/ruby-processing/tree/master

== Preprcessing/Run

結構めんどい

* create artist_data.json and artworks
	$ cscript create_data.js > data/artist_data.json
* change playlist name in js scripts: play_itunes.js, get_tracks.js, create_data.js
	var PLAYLIST_NAME = " "; // set your playlist name
* run sketch
	$ rp5 run treemap_player.rb

== Reference

* ビジュアライジングデータ http://oreilly.com/catalog/9780596514556/
* Ben Fry さん http://benfry.com/writing/archives/3
